3. cs.SE (Software Engineering) is another possible category as the paper discusses the practical implementation of AI ethics in software development.
4. cs.RO (Robotics) is a possible category as the paper may discuss the ethical considerations in the development of AI-powered robots in industrial settings.
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper may discuss the security and privacy implications of AI systems in industrial settings.
